name: Strobuster
overview: Released in Italy as Labirinto and published in Commodore Club N°07 and Digital Marketing PD #025 / a.k.a. "Bomb Jack Junior". It is your task to recover the various objects littered around the playing screen, flying from one platform to another. Be careful not to fall! In one of the Italian releases named Vampir, and published in Nova Games n.28 (Febbraio 1989), it identifies your character as a friendly Vampire.
